snippet: Rising Austrian star Dominic Thiem reached the quarterfinals of the Rio Open on Wednesday with a 7-5, 7-5 victory over Argentina's Diego Schwartzman....
lead_paragraph: Rising Austrian star Dominic Thiem reached the quarterfinals of the Rio Open on Wednesday with a 7-5, 7-5 victory over Argentina's Diego Schwartzman.

headline.print_headline: Thiem Reaches Quarterfinals in Rio; Tsonga Out on Rainy Day
